== 剧情 ==
该剧講述1980后年轻人在赡养父母、婚姻問題及抚养幼兒等压力下引发的現今社会话题。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://enjoy.eastday.com/e/20130509/u1a7380000.html |title=六六质疑《小儿难养》:某些场景和电视剧不相干 |access-date=2013-05-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714152424/http://enjoy.eastday.com/e/20130509/u1a7380000.html |archive-date=2014-07-14 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

